com.canoo.dolphin.server.config

Class DolphinPlatformConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.canoo.dolphin.server.config.DolphinPlatformConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DolphinPlatformConfiguration
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class defines the configuration of the Dolphin Platform. Normally the configuration is created based on defaults and a property file (see ConfigurationFileLoader).
